//ARTICOLO CUFFIE
The Headphone market is living a big changing era: personal assistants like Alexa, Google Assistant and Siri, the bluetooth, and the noise
reduction feature are literally forcing all the big brands to invest in research and technology in order to provide their products
with all these awesome features that will make our life easier day after day.

The counter part? Well, maybe the price, but it's understandable. The quality of the speaker from brand like Bose, Sennheiser, B & W, Beats 
is incredible and yes, you have to pay for it.

The only great thing of this market is its variety, you can have good headphones starting from 20 € till the best ones around 350/400 €.
Different shapes and format, bluetooth or cable, in-ear, on-ear, over-ear, sometimes i think that who wants to buy a new headphones has
to study a bit in order to understand what is buying.

Here a selection of really good headphones of all the typologies and prices!

